We are looking for an innovative software engineer to help us build the future!


This position will:

\u2022 Create new features and fix bugs

\u2022 Collaborate with the product owner and other developers

\u2022 Operate with minimal oversight to develop code the matches provided requirements


The preferred candidate has:

\u2022 Desire to contribute energy to building great technology solutions

\u2022 Entrepreneurial, collaborative spirit needed to work in a distributed startup culture

\u2022 Practical experience designing scalable applications for web and/or mobile

\u2022 Effective verbal, written communication skills

\u2022 Experience with Angular, Node, and MongoDB required


This is not an entry-level position - you need to be able to hit the ground running.

However, capabilities are far more important than credentials.


This is a full-time (W-2), 100% remote position.

Candidates in Florida, Ohio, or Utah are preferred.

Private Auto LLC offers employees medical and dental insurance.
